citations:
  citation-awoiaf-donal-noye:
    source: source-awoiaf
    properties:
      locator: "Donal Noye"
      accessed: "2026-03-15"
    notes: "Born before 252 AC in the Stormlands. Died 300 AC at Castle Black. Stormlander culture. Allegiance: Night's Watch (formerly House Baratheon). One-armed armorer and steward. Forged Robert's warhammer at Storm's End. Lost his arm during the siege of Storm's End in Robert's Rebellion. Died defending the gate against the giant Mag the Mighty during the battle of Castle Black."
